    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Caius</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルビア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rubia</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ガイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guy</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんつうかお前って
戦ってる時とか犬みてぇだよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You know, you're like a dog when you fight.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだと！？
オレが獣人だから、バカにしてるのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What did you say?!
Are you making fun of me for being a beastman?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちょ、ちょっとカイウス。
落ち着きなさいよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wa-Wait a second, Caius.
Calm down!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルーク、あまりそういう事を言うな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Luke, don't say rude things like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんでだよ？
犬っぽく見えたからそう言って
なにがいけねぇんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why not?
I just said it 'cause he looked like a dog.
What's so bad about it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>犬、犬って、いい加減にしろよ！
今すぐ勝負だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Enough with calling me a dog!
We're settling this right now with a battle!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ？　なに怒ってんだよ。
マジ意味わかんねーし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? What're you so mad about?
I seriously don't get this.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ……そりゃ怒るだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haa... Of course he's angry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
